<p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27.857px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); line-height: 2.29em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为学习贯彻</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); text-indent: 41px; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">习近平总书记的“青年观”，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27.857px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">经济管理学院党支部于2023年12月7日下午18时在314党员活动室召开“总书记的青年观”主题学习会议。此次会议由经济管理学院学生支部汪薇同志主持，学生党员参加。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27.857px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240113/1705116788397076028.png" title="1705116788397076028.png" alt="c6377dbef8f8672d939da571a664a14e.png" width="967" height="387" style="width: 967px; height: 387px;"/></span></p>